### ============================================
### BDFM RAG System API Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001/api/rag
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/rag
@userId = 0199dcde-0a99-7c9a-bb26-4dbcd064579c
@conversationId = 7855b184-f0e6-4097-9ee2-3b183b359be9

### ============================================
### 1. RAG Query Endpoints
### ============================================

### 1.1 Query the RAG system
POST {{baseUrl}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "ما هي أنواع المعاملات المتاحة؟",
  "maxResults": 5,
  "similarityThreshold": 0.7,
  "includeMetadata": true
}

### 1.2 Query with streaming response
POST {{baseUrl}}/query/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "اشرح لي سير العمل في النظام",
  "maxResults": 3,
  "similarityThreshold": 0.6
}

### 1.3 Search without LLM generation
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "معاملات واردة",
  "maxResults": 10,
  "similarityThreshold": 0.5
}

### ============================================
### 2. Conversation Endpoints
### ============================================

### 2.1 Create a new conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "title": "محادثة حول سير العمل",
  "metadata": {
    "topic": "workflow",
    "language": "ar"
  }
}

### 2.2 List all conversations for a user
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations?userId={{userId}}&limit=50&offset=0

### 2.3 Get a specific conversation with all messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}?userId={{userId}}

### 2.4 Send a message in a conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "message": "كيف يمكنني إنشاء معاملة جديدة؟",
  "maxResults": 5,
  "similarityThreshold": 0.7
}

### 2.5 Send message with streaming response
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations/message/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "{{conversationId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "message": "اشرح لي خطوات الموافقة على المعاملة",
  "maxResults": 3
}

### 2.6 Update conversation title
PUT {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/title
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "title": "محادثة محدثة - سير العمل"
}

### 2.7 Delete a conversation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}?userId={{userId}}

### ============================================
### 3. Speech-to-Text Endpoints
### ============================================

### 3.1 Transcribe audio file to text
POST {{baseUrl}}/speech/transcribe
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="audio.mp3"
Content-Type: audio/mpeg

< ./path/to/audio.mp3
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="language"

ar
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 3.2 Transcribe audio from URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/speech/transcribe-url
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://example.com/audio.mp3",
  "language": "ar"
}

### 3.3 Send voice message in conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/speech/voice-message
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="voice.mp3"
Content-Type: audio/mpeg

< ./path/to/voice.mp3
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

{{userId}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="language"

ar
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="maxResults"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 3.4 Send voice message with streaming
POST {{baseUrl}}/speech/voice-message/stream
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="voice.mp3"
Content-Type: audio/mpeg

< ./path/to/voice.mp3
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

{{userId}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 3.5 Get supported audio formats
GET {{baseUrl}}/speech/formats

### 3.6 Detect language from audio
POST {{baseUrl}}/speech/detect-language
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="audio.mp3"
Content-Type: audio/mpeg

< ./path/to/audio.mp3
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### ============================================
### 4. Statistics Endpoints - Correspondences
### ============================================

### 4.1 Get correspondence statistics overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/correspondences/overview

### 4.2 Get correspondence statistics with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/correspondences/overview?dateFrom=2025-01-01&dateTo=2025-10-29&correspondenceType=incoming,outgoing&priorityLevel=high,urgent&secrecyLevel=confidential&userId={{userId}}

### 4.3 Get correspondence time series data - Daily
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/correspondences/time-series?period=day

### 4.4 Get correspondence time series data - Weekly
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/correspondences/time-series?period=week&dateFrom=2025-09-01&dateTo=2025-10-29

### 4.5 Get correspondence time series data - Monthly
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/correspondences/time-series?period=month&dateFrom=2025-01-01&dateTo=2025-10-29

### 4.6 Get correspondence time series data - Yearly
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/correspondences/time-series?period=year

### ============================================
### 5. Statistics Endpoints - Workflow
### ============================================

### 5.1 Get workflow statistics overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/workflow/overview

### 5.2 Get workflow statistics with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/workflow/overview?dateFrom=2025-01-01&dateTo=2025-10-29&status=pending,in_progress,completed&userId={{userId}}

### 5.3 Get workflow tracking for a correspondence
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/workflow/tracking/CORR-123

### 5.4 Get overdue workflow steps
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/workflow/overdue

### 5.5 Get overdue workflow steps for specific user
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/workflow/overdue?userId={{userId}}

### ============================================
### 6. Statistics Endpoints - Reports
### ============================================

### 6.1 Get performance report
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/reports/performance?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-10-29

### 6.2 Get performance report for specific user
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/reports/performance?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-10-29&userId={{userId}}

### 6.3 Get user productivity statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/users/{{userId}}/productivity?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-10-29

### 6.4 Clear statistics cache
POST {{baseUrl}}/statistics/cache/clear

### ============================================
### 7. System Health & Status
### ============================================

### 7.1 Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 7.2 Get system status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status

### ============================================
### Notes:
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Replace {{baseUrl}} with your actual API base URL
### 2. Replace {{userId}} and {{conversationId}} with actual IDs
### 3. For file uploads, replace ./path/to/audio.mp3 with actual file path
### 4. Streaming endpoints return Server-Sent Events (SSE)
### 5. All Arabic text in requests should be UTF-8 encoded
### 6. Timeout is set to 120000ms (2 minutes) for AI operations
### 
### Supported Audio Formats:
### - MP3, WAV, M4A, OGG, WEBM, FLAC
### - Max file size: typically 25MB
### - Max duration: typically 30 minutes
### 
### Date Format: ISO 8601 (YYYY-MM-DD or YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ss.sssZ)
### 
### Response Format: All endpoints return:
### {
###   "success": boolean,
###   "data": any,
###   "error": { "message": string, "code": string } | null
### }
### ============================================
